  <brief_title>Alemtuzumab in Treating Patients With Waldenstrom's Macroglobulinemia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Study of Campath-1H in Lymphoplasmacytic Lymphoma (Waldenstrom's Macroglobulinemia)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
